---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Umar Yunusa" description="Learn more about Umar Yunusa: Senior Backend Engineer, open source creator, AI engineer, and founder of Real Dev.">
	<section class="space-y-8 py-4">
		<div>
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl mb-6">
				About Me
			</h1>
		</div>

		<!-- Biography Section -->
		<div class="prose">
			<blockquote class="my-6 border-l-4 border-accent-custom pl-4 italic text-muted-custom">
				I got into programming by building things before I fully understood what I was building. Over 7+ years I've shipped fintech systems handling 500K+ daily transactions, built AI-integrated platforms before it was fashionable, and spent nights launching open-source tools just to scratch my own itch. I write mostly about backend systems, AI engineering, and the craft of building software that lasts.
			</blockquote>

			<p>
				I am a software engineer with 7+ years of experience specialized in constructing robust backend systems, scaling microservices, and orchestrating production AI workflows. I design high-throughput systems, contribute to open-source developer tooling, and write about the engineering of reliable software.
			</p>
			
			<p>
				My career spans working with international companies in South Korea, Canada, and Nigeria. I have worked across a wide spectrum of systems—from full-stack web applications and custom WordPress architectures to highly distributed, event-driven Node.js/TypeScript microservices and Python AI/RAG pipelines.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Facts Section -->
		<div class="pt-6 border-t border-border-custom">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Quick Facts</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span><strong>7+ years</strong> of professional engineering experience across Nigeria, South Korea (MUST Company), and Canada (Manaknight Digital).</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span><strong>Lead Backend Engineer at MUST Company</strong> — overseeing migration from PHP to NestJS/TypeScript microservices and event-driven architectures.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Built production <strong>AI & RAG systems</strong> integrating Claude, OpenAI, and Gemini with vector databases (Pinecone, ChromaDB) for intelligent document intelligence.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Founder of <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@real_dev_hq" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-custom hover:underline font-semibold">Real Dev</a> — a developer talk show launched in <strong>2026</strong>.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Currently building <strong class="text-fg-custom">LLMesh</strong> (launched in <strong>2026</strong>), an open-source PHP AI SDK: <em>"The PHP AI SDK — works everywhere, including Laravel."</em></span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Creator of <strong class="text-fg-custom">Aura CSS</strong> (<code>useaura</code> on npm, launched in <strong>2026</strong>) — a lightweight semantic attribute-based CSS library with over 1,000+ weekly downloads.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>B.Sc. in <strong>Computer Science</strong> from the University of Ibadan, Oyo State, Nigeria.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
					<span class="text-accent-custom select-none">&rarr;</span>
					<span>Shipped <strong class="text-fg-custom">Omni File</strong> (in <strong>2026</strong>), osbts (npm), Wazobia AI Agent, PromptGuard, and PromptLint.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
